    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="columns">
      <p>I'm a <a href="/are-we-small-yet">computer programmer</a> and recovering <a href="/a-shrinking-feeling">musician</a> and <a href="/3d-studio-max">artist</a> from Canada. This website is an archive of playful things I made for myself and others. Some of it might chance to delight you, but at the very least, surely none of it will cause permanent discomfort.</p>
      <p>Where to start? Well you can keep reading this page to learn more about me. Or, jump directly to the projects <a href="/types">by type</a> or <a href="/time">by time</a>. I advise checking out <a href="/2013">2013</a>, which was one of my more productive years.</p>
